# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Parquet cache
#   bronze/  — COMMITTED to git so GitHub Actions has the baseline scrape
#              (Sofascore is Cloudflare-blocked on datacenter IPs; local
#              developer commits fresh Parquets after each manual pull)
#   silver/  — derived; rebuilt by build_features.py every nightly run
#   gold/    — reserved for future aggregates; always derivable
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
data/silver/
data/gold/

